wDr6ucdGZgXGGAOBDxVO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=37d0f4fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200301/15/0115178.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n《駐軍法》第九條，香港駐軍不干預香港特別行政區的地方事務。<br />\n<br />\n香港駐軍人員違反軍隊紀律的，給予紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n即係自己圍內紀律處分搞撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba58107ca5ddf457116bca39f4842460b913623","tid":862489,"uid":55032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"扮乜撚野義工垃圾佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   去裝野咋 呢招真係高"},{"pid":"f18729564616ba6b8507f7c6bfb29527c40d1213","tid":862489,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"哈，終於開始做出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快會出現幫手救下貓狗，再黎就救下困𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610240ac3740c726cd81ff5c965c06a5de535a18","tid":862489,"uid":94454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bba58107ca5ddf457116bca39f4842460b913623","tid":862489,"uid":55032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"扮乜撚野義工垃圾佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   去裝野咋 呢招真係高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:36:57.000Z","msg":"連行山都要比人偷聽監視<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff31ae7524ba13281f99054e83be490bb4581aed","tid":862489,"uid":140454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"解放軍應該只係容許係軍營摺被"}]}